        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, which has made him wonder whether his shyness in public until the age of 55 resulted from fear of subjecting his face to ridicule.</p>  
<p>Criticises F. Galton’s <hi rend="italic">Hereditary genius</hi> [1869] for neglecting environmental influence.</p> 
